---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/landing.css';
import '../styles/for-drivers.css';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Drive for Attic — Denver driver jobs"
  description="W-2 driver jobs in Denver: $28/hr, 6–8 hour shifts, home every night. We provide the truck, fuel, and maintenance. Apply in two minutes."
  ogTitle="Drive with Attic — Denver driver jobs"
  ogDescription="Short routes. Real pay. Good trucks."
>

<header class="drv-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="drv-hero__grid">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Drive with Attic · Denver</p>
        <h1>Short routes.<br/><em>Real pay.</em><br/>Good trucks.</h1>
        <p class="lede">We're hiring Denver drivers to pick up, deliver, and hand back the bins that matter to our customers. No long-haul. No surge games.</p>
        <div class="hero__cta">
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="mailto:drive@attic.it.com?subject=Driver%20application">Apply in 2 minutes</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg" href="#requirements">Requirements →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <dl class="drv-hero__card">
        <div class="drv-hero__row"><dt>Pay</dt><dd><em>$28</em> / hour</dd></div>
        <div class="drv-hero__row"><dt>Tips</dt><dd>100% to driver</dd></div>
        <div class="drv-hero__row"><dt>Shift length</dt><dd>6–8 hrs</dd></div>
        <div class="drv-hero__row"><dt>Route radius</dt><dd>Denver metro</dd></div>
        <div class="drv-hero__row"><dt>Truck</dt><dd>We provide</dd></div>
        <div class="drv-hero__row"><dt>Benefits</dt><dd>W-2 · health · PTO</dd></div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="stripe stripe--paper">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div style="max-width:680px;margin-bottom:48px;">
      <p class="eyebrow">Why Attic</p>
      <h2 class="h2">A driving job that <em>respects your day.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="drv-perks">
      <div class="drv-perk">
        <div class="drv-perk__icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Fixed shifts, not a gig app</h3>
        <p>You're a W-2 employee. You know when you're working and when you're home. No pinging you at 9pm.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="drv-perk">
        <div class="drv-perk__icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M1 3h15v13H1z"/><path d="M16 8h4l3 3v5h-7"/><circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Our truck, our fuel</h3>
        <p>Drive a well-maintained sprinter van out of our Denver facility. We cover gas, maintenance, and insurance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="drv-perk">
        <div class="drv-perk__icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Home every night</h3>
        <p>Every route starts and ends in Denver. You sleep in your own bed. Weekends are optional, not mandatory.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="stripe drv-day">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="drv-day__grid">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">A Tuesday in the life</p>
        <h2 class="h2">Route, not rodeo.</h2>
        <p class="body-lg" style="margin-top:20px;">Most drivers run a single route of 12–18 stops a day. Pickups in the morning, deliveries in the afternoon, done by 5.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="drv-day__list">
        <div class="drv-day__item"><div class="drv-day__time">8:00 AM</div><div class="drv-day__what"><h4>Clock in at the facility</h4><p>Coffee, load the van with today's bins, scan them in.</p></div></div>
        <div class="drv-day__item"><div class="drv-day__time">8:45 AM</div><div class="drv-day__what"><h4>First drop-off</h4><p>4 empty bins to a household in Highland. 10 minutes.</p></div></div>
        <div class="drv-day__item"><div class="drv-day__time">11:30 AM</div><div class="drv-day__what"><h4>Pickup in Wash Park</h4><p>6 packed bins. Scan, load, drive.</p></div></div>
        <div class="drv-day__item"><div class="drv-day__time">12:30 PM</div><div class="drv-day__what"><h4>Lunch</h4><p>Paid. Your choice of spot.</p></div></div>
        <div class="drv-day__item"><div class="drv-day__time">3:15 PM</div><div class="drv-day__what"><h4>Return deliveries</h4><p>Four neighborhoods, nine stops. Back to the attic by 5.</p></div></div>
        <div class="drv-day__item"><div class="drv-day__time">5:00 PM</div><div class="drv-day__what"><h4>Done</h4><p>Scan everything off the van. Clock out. See you tomorrow.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="requirements" class="stripe">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="drv-req">
      <div class="drv-req__grid">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Who we're looking for</p>
          <h2 class="h2" style="margin-top:8px;">Good drivers.<br/><em>Good humans.</em></h2>
          <p class="body" style="margin-top:20px;max-width:380px;">Our drivers are the face of Attic. Customers see us at their front door — we want people who are calm, careful, and friendly there.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Requirements</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>21+ with a valid Colorado driver's license</li>
            <li>Clean MVR (no major infractions in 3 years)</li>
            <li>Able to lift 60 lbs comfortably, repeatedly</li>
            <li>Smartphone (iOS 15+ or Android 11+)</li>
            <li>Authorization to work in the U.S.</li>
            <li>Good vibes at the door. This matters.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:40px;padding-top:32px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <p class="body" style="margin:0;">Application takes about two minutes. We respond within 48 hours.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="mailto:drive@attic.it.com?subject=Driver%20application">Apply now →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
